# Kate & Ari's Wedding Website

A static wedding website for Kate and Ari's celebration at the Ashokan Center, October 17-19, 2025. This website is designed to be hosted on GitHub Pages.

## Features

- Responsive design that works on all devices
- Custom navigation with a curvy braid design
- Informational pages about the venue, accommodations, and schedule
- RSVP functionality through an embedded Google Form

